# Per-user config for minds / fct tooling. Copy to apps/minds/.env (which is
# gitignored) and fill in. Read by `just sync-vendor-mngr`, `just fct-worktree`,
# and `just bake-slice-dev`; also COPY'd into each mngr agent worktree (see
# .mngr/settings.toml work_dir_extra_paths). Nothing personal is committed.

# Absolute path to your forever-claude-template checkout. Edit to wherever you
# cloned it -- the example is the common ~/project location, which is not where
# everyone keeps it. Optional for `just fct-worktree`: it only speeds the clone
# (borrows objects); a missing/wrong path just falls back to a remote clone.
# Required by `bake-slice-dev` and a minds release (apps/minds/docs/release.md,
# step 3), which need a real local checkout at this path.
FCT_DIR=$HOME/project/forever-claude-template
